thumbnail = "NovoTerm - Serial Terminal for Firmware Developers"
snippet="NovoTerm is a desktop app that helps firmware developers view incoming/outgoing serial data in various formats and also send data easily. You can save data sequences and send them whenever needed. Data can be exported easily."
+++
No ads and no credit card required. All features are available in the free version.
The only limitation is on the amount of data you can export to txt/cvs file and on the number of data sequences you can have in the app. 
